  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d8b\u0dc3\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dc5\u0da7 \u2019\u2019B\u2019\u2019 03\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dad\u0dca  \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dd4 14 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db1\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "14-year-old Dewum Sanahas who got 03 B's in high school",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 14-year-old child has succeeded in setting a record in the country by appearing in the last 2021 General Certificate of Studies (Higher Level) examination under the commercial stream and passing with three \"B\" grades.",
        "This child named \"Dewum Sanahas Ranasinghe\" who is currently studying in the 9th grade of Nanamal International School, Kadavata, Mawaramandiya, passed G.E.C. in the 8th grade. (Ordinary Text) Examination and obtained \"A\" passes - 6, \"B\" passes - 2 and \"C\" passes - 1.",
        "This child, who has managed to score 173 marks in the five-year scholarship, has appeared in the general examination at the age of 13.",
        "Student Sanahas, who resides in Lower Imbulgoda area, Gampaha, is the eldest child in a family of three children, and his mother, Mrs. Malka Ranasinghe, and father, Mr. Anura Ranasinghe, have left the government teaching service and work as teachers at the international school where Sanahas studies.",
        "Mrs. Ranasinghe stated that she will discuss with the University Grants Commission whether it is possible to admit this child to a public university and if that is not possible, she intends to find out whether there is a possibility to admit the child to a private university.",
        "The mother further stated that her child appeared in the last high-level examination and used the internet to gain awareness about certain subjects during the last corona epidemic. Although she did not participate in tutoring classes, a group of teachers in the school, where she was studying, provided maximum support to the child in his studies. And done.",
        "She and her husband have provided the necessary support and strength since the time when she said that she wanted to appear for the general level and advanced level exams even though she did not meet the required age limits since she showed her skills in various fields since she was small. Mrs. Malka Ranasinghe (mother) continued.",
        "Dewum Sanahas Ranasinghe, a student who has achieved many feats in cricket, said that he is hoping to join the national cricket team. He said that his future hope is to work in the field of law. This child who shows abilities in speaking and writing is more talented than his age."
      ],
